Text: Ameritrade Email Satisfaction Survey KMMCKMValued Ameritrade Customer You recently contacted Ameritrade Customer Service by email We appreciate you using this channel to contact us To assist us in continuing to improve our level of service we ask that you take a moment to participate in an online survey Your response will be kept completely confidential To complete the survey simply click on the link below custsurveyACSSurveycgia If you are unable to click on the link above copy and paste the link address directly into the address area of your browser We appreciate your prompt response to our survey Thank you for your time and assistance Ameritrade values your patronage and your privacy Ameritrade will not sell rent or otherwise distribute your email address to other companies If you would prefer that Ameritrade not send you email like this in the future please reply to this email with the word Unsubscribe in the subject line
